## Description {#details}

Helper structure to be able to read SetCC information.

If set to true, IsAArch64 field, Info is a <a href="/docs/api/structs/aarch64setccinfo">AArch64SetCCInfo</a>, otherwise Info is a <a href="/docs/api/structs/genericsetccinfo">GenericSetCCInfo</a>.
